######################################################
# Databeses needed for crsim
# Created by M Oue 2023.08.16
######################################################

LLUTS3: Lookup dables from scattering calculations
P3: Database needed for WRF P3 (MP50) 
SBM_20: Database needed for WRF SBM (MP20)

Before running crsim, please download the tar-zipped scattering calculation lookup table files from:

and untar/unzip them under ./LLUTS3/.

Each tar-zipped file includes a directory containing scattering database files.
The untarred directories should be placed under ./LLUTS3. So, LLUTS3 should contain:
ceilo/
cloud/
gh_ryzh/
graupel/
graupel_ar0.60/
graupel_ar0.80/
ice_ar0.20/
ice_ar0.90/
mpl/
partrimedice/
partrimedice_ar0.40/
partrimedice_ar0.60/
partrimedice_ar0.80/
raina/
rainb/
smallice/
snow_ar0.60/
unrimedice/
unrimedice_ar0.40/
unrimedice_ar0.60/
unrimedice_ar0.80/


